//// Does not include compilation when android related stuff is used. Just simple raw kotlin code that can also be run in console

o Compiling kotlin files from the command line / terminal
// I will start with the steps, then with the code to follow
- First create the .jar file
- Then run the .jar file
> kotlin someKotlinFile.kt -include-runtime -d resultingJarFile.jar		// created the jar
> java -jar resultingJarFile.jar										// runs the jar
